<plot>When inner-city couple Cathy Redstone and her husband, Chris, have a marital rift, each falls into the arms of another. Chris is comforted then seduced by his manipulative Swedish best friend, Magnus, who claims to be straight and is really after Cathy. Cathy, in turn, is comforted and seduced by her half-brother, Stan Redstone (so it's only "half as bad.") The only way to resolve these complications is for the 2 new couples to embark on a foursome! And that's where the real romance begins. Snapshot is a hilarious and dark exploration of intimacy, commitment, marriage, love and lust, and the true nature of romance. Can these four "idealists" sustain their newfound love?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?503114</url></doc>
